      <acqinfo id="aspace_6e354819cd1617656cfc9e5bbae44199">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The Yates Family Papers were purchased in 1968 from the Winterthur Museum, which had acquired them from the estate of Helen Delancy Watkins of Schenectady, N.Y.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
